            <p class="intro">
                Discover a one-of-a-kind venue in the region! Alyasa Village boasts beautiful weather at an altitude of
                1100m, just 30 minutes away from Byblos. Our unique setting includes a historic church neighbored by old
                oak trees, dedicated to the Prophet Alishaa.
